Hellplague:
 
While Celeron was busy with cleaning up, Hellplague began cleaning up the computer, reorganizing files and de bugging programs.  she was putting the logs into a file folder when Celeron finished.  She knew he'd come to ask if there would be anything else to do.  She had to stop and think if there was anything else he could do...

rm2kmidi <kraftlos@...> wrote:
He nodded and left the room....  At least it was somthing to do.

He went accross the ship and found all the scraps and spare parts and
brought them back to the storage room.  It took him at least a couple
of hours...


"HA!  Is that all you got?  You boasted such power, such skill!  Where is your power and skill now?  You disappoint me, ha ha ha haa!"
